				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id="menu-content-step2" class="menu-content">
		<div class="card text-white bg-secondary mb-3 card-ovrwr">
			<div class="card-header">Spread</div>
			<div class="card-body">
				<p class="card-text mt-2">
					I have found a way to expand my army. Now follow in my footsteps and conquer 
